Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.66,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Pai! Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:52.30,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Pai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:14.63,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,"Do you know anything about the starry skies of the past?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:18.26,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,"Do you have any memories of them?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:22.22,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Is this the topic of the questionnaire?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.97,DTB-Default,Mother,0,0,0,,It's a strange topic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:28.02,DTB-Default,Mother,0,0,0,,It's probably because of the rumor about the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:29.21,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:31.48,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,That's right! It's today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:35.82,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,You can see the stars of the past for one night. Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:37.66,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Stars of the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.99,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,From midnight until dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:45.20,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No way. We're not talking about  happy hour at Kabukicho, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:02:07.12,Location,,0,0,0,,{\be1\bord0\shad0\fs30\c&H2F2F2F&\pos(640,171)}This month's goal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:02:07.12,Location,,0,0,0,,{\be1\bord0\shad0\fs30\c&H2F2F2F&\pos(640,222)}on our loan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:02:07.12,Location,,0,0,0,,{\be1\bord0\shad0\fs30\c&H6643B6&\pos(640,197)}Bonus payment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:50.61,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,N-n-n-n-no! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:54.12,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,In any case, what you want me to do for this brat... I-I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:56.77,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,your son, is conduct a survey, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:02:02.52,DTB-Default,Mother,0,0,0,,Even these kinds of extra credit  assignments can affect his grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:07.53,DTB-Default,Mother,0,0,0,,The more the better, as far as this assignment is concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:10.98,DTB-Default,Mother,0,0,0,,Other children will probably collect ten replies at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:14.36,DTB-Default,Mother,0,0,0,,So let's make it fifty... no, a hundred for my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.61,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:18.90,DTB-Default,Mother,0,0,0,,Obtain a hundred replies for this questionnaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.57,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.28,DTB-Default,Mother,0,0,0,,I'll pay 100,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:28.75,DTB-Default,Mother,0,0,0,,Just because it's a child's homework assignment  doesn't mean it's acceptable for my Yoshihiro-chan to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:35.42,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Even so, homework should be done by yourse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:49.02,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,We'll get a hundred responses!  Let us take care of this assignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:52.40,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Leave it to the Kurasawa Detective Agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:58.82,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,I hope you didn't have a personal relationship with November 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.78,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Nothing aside from a professional one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:07.43,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Decade had good reason to be concerned.  There's little doubt November 11 was a member of the E.P.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:11.21,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Did the E.P.R. have any motive to kill Decade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:16.39,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,This case is no longer within our jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:18.55,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Don't probe into this matter any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.51,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Actions taken by PANDORA were rather aggressive the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.64,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,very uncharacteristic of a research facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:26.98,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Since when has PANDORA...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:28.97,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear what I said, Kirihara?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:32.48,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,This case is out of our jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.82,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,It was simply another case involving the death of a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.09,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,He was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:42.40,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,He was someone who took pride in himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:44.87,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Whether he was a contractor or not had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:48.11,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,His last words were...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:50.85,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,"Do what you believe is right."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:52.67,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:55.21,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Wait! Did he contact you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.46,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,That was just a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:10.18,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That area in South America has been  off-limits ever since the incident occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:15.09,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,The only thing we know for sure is  that massive warfare broke out around it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.04,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,which was on the scale of a world war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:23.17,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,During the conflict,  myriads of contractors were deployed as weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:27.04,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hei and Amber were among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.95,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,They were assigned by the same syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:36.56,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It was said that Hei wasn't a contractor when he earned his reputation as the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:37.72,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:41.21,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There was another contractor who was widely feared, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:45.17,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,The one named Pai, Hei's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:05.32,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Is she still in the middle of her remuneration?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:10.35,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,You two are always together. You look like lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.19,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Are you gazing at the stars again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:17.55,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Only because I don't have anything else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:24.99,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,No matter how long you stare at them,  you won't be able to see the stars of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:48.95,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Yes. According to Schroeder,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:47.43,Location,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad5\fnArial\fs55\fscx80\c&H315246&\frz31.361\4c&H6CBB9D&\move(717,410,710,410)}Secret line
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:47.97,Location,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad5\fnArial\fs55\fscx80\c&H315246&\frz31.361\4c&H6CBB9D&\move(709,410,702,410)}Secret line
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:48.51,Location,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad5\fnArial\fs55\fscx80\c&H315246&\frz31.361\4c&H6CBB9D&\move(701,410,694,410)}Secret line
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:48.97,Location,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad5\fnArial\fs55\fscx80\c&H315246&\frz31.361\4c&H6CBB9D&\move(692,410,686,410)}Secret line
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.85,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,the light emitted by the masked contractor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:55.02,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,and the light observed prior to the  disappearance of the gate in South America
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:58.22,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,are believed to be the one in the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.75,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Light, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:04.30,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was an intense light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.84,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.68,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,I realized why Amber needs Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:13.55,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,She wants to replicate what happened in South America,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:17.18,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,and she probably needs Hei's power to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:21.85,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Are you saying there's a connection between Hei  and the disappearance of the South American gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:26.74,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute. If what you say is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:32.32,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,The contractor's identity has been confirmed to be BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:38.92,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Yes, I've already made the  arrangements for the elimination of his unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:41.42,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,The stars of the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.29,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Yes, the stars from the distant past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:47.38,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Anything is fine.  Please try to recall anything that comes to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.41,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Stars are stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:54.19,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,I can't tell the difference between  the stars of the past and the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:56.32,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,}Sir, do you have something to add?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:59.26,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Anything about the stars or the night skies of the past is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:01.95,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,You're wasting your time on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.36,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,He's not the talkative type.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:07.57,DTB-Default,Husband,0,0,0,,I get nostalgic whenever I think  about the night of the Giacobinids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.50,DTB-Default,Husband,0,0,0,,It's been thirty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:14.90,DTB-Default,Husband,0,0,0,,No... Since Toshikyuki was still in elementary school back then, it's been longer than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.91,DTB-Default,Husband,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:20.43,DTB-Default,Husband,0,0,0,,He insisted on watching the meteor shower,  so I drove him out in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:23.64,DTB-Default,Husband,0,0,0,,We waited for quite a while, but we never saw it that evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.67,DTB-Default,Husband,0,0,0,,In the end, he fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.80,DTB-Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}To those of you who plan to go outside soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.42,DTB-Default,Wang,0,0,0,,No, I haven't made any plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.42,DTB-Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Rie has some tips for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:34.30,DTB-Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Although it's still overcast, showers are expected later in  the evening, so make sure to bring an umbrella with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.94,DTB-Default,Wang,0,0,0,,I just don't have the time to be gazing at the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:37.75,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,It looks like it might be called off.  The forecast says it's going to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:42.72,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,The skies aren't going to be clear?  We won't be able to see the stars of the past, will we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:45.02,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Do you believe in it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.46,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,Well, who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:50.00,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Not that rumor again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:54.16,DTB-Default,Wang,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I do have some memories of the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.93,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,What kind of memories? Something romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.31,DTB-Default,Wang,0,0,0,,No, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:03.22,DTB-Default,Wang,0,0,0,,Do you remember when you were about this tall?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:05.98,DTB-Default,Wang,0,0,0,,You got lost in an amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.88,DTB-Default,Wang,0,0,0,,By the time I found you, it was already dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:13.26,DTB-Default,Wang,0,0,0,,I was scared to death, but you kept a straight face and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.81,DTB-Default,Wang,0,0,0,,"I was watching the stars".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.89,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,You're kidding! I was really cute, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:23.27,DTB-Default,Wang,0,0,0,,You sure were.  That happened while your mother was still well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:54.63,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,That was a pretty horrible attempt  at tailing somebody, Saitou, Kouno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:59.87,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this? Who ordered you to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.59,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Er... That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:08.28,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,If you were ordered to follow me,  you should have asked Ohtsuka to do it in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.48,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.38,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Li-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:40.26,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.34,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,U-Um... Are you hungry by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:51.59,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(968,323)}Episode Twenty-Three
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:51.59,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(968,526)}God is In His Heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.40,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Did I look that hungry to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:02.17,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Well, sort of. You looked like someone I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:05.70,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Did I look like the criminal you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:10.14,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I was right, just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:11.55,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.21,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:18.47,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Someone's trying to snipe you from the seats in the aft.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.81,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Come on. That wasn't convincing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.55,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:29.69,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:45.69,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,It's a strange feeling.  When you've chased suspects for as long as I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:48.10,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,you develop an attachment to what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:50.75,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Always on the job, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.34,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,It's true that I've put in a lot of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:57.63,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,but after a while,  you become another face in the crowd to the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:00.14,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,It feels like I've lost a part of my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.07,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Every organization is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:06.60,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,They treat you like a pawn and exploit you at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.02,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:13.61,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Like I said, it's not that I can't pay the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:17.28,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I'm just short on cash right now, so I'll pay you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:20.20,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Sir, your name is on our blacklist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.38,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,If I recall, you pulled the same stunt last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.11,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You must be kidding!  You must have mistaken me for someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:30.30,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Right. There's no way my boss could  afford to come to a place like this very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.46,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,No way! Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.67,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I'm shocked. I didn't know you liked middle-aged women!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.93,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,M-Middle-aged...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.64,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Li-kun! Your timing couldn't have been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.17,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:53.25,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Yeah, any memories about the stars of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:56.28,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,People sure like to talk about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:58.73,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Memories tend to become exaggerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.47,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Well, taking the emergence of the gate and everything else into consideration,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.32,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I suppose it's a result of their insecurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.03,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Insecurity?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:07.53,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,The recent terrorist attack, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:12.85,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,People appear to be calm and collected,  but I'm sure they're insecure about the present,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.24,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,which is why they rely on their memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:21.05,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,This is where we part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:24.43,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You saved my ass. Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:28.61,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?  Make sure you pay me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.26,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.57,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Isn't it a wonderful sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:57.88,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.27,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,How do you feel about this city? Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.98,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Well, it's not that I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.07,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,It's moderately indifferent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:08.56,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,yet moderately warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.66,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I wasn't supposed to stay here as long as I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:15.94,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,but now I wish I could make it my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:20.94,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I see. This city is getting more violent by the day, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:23.98,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,This city is serene
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:27.29,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,compared to the tragedy my sister and I lived through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:30.02,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Were you in a combat zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:37.08,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,How about your sister? Is she still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:39.02,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No, she isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:40.98,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Did she pass away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.23,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,That must have been a sad moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.54,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.07,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,A part of me might have felt relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:57.38,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Have you heard about the rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:00.62,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I have, but I don't think it's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:04.22,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I didn't think anyone would believe it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.50,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Oh, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.97,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Do you think we'll be able to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.01,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:42.39,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Is everyone going to wait until the skies  clear up just to catch a glimpse of the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.76,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Do you want to see the stars of the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:50.22,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I do, but I want to show it to others even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:55.22,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,It won't happen unless the stars  of the present fade away, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.80,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,They weren't real to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:04.63,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,True, but if those stars were to disappear all at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.31,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I think it'd be sad in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.82,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I have to go. I'm glad we were able to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.92,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I was thinking about too many things  and wasn't sure about what I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:27.28,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,When you're not sure about something, you should just trust your intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.32,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Was it something I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.21,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,No, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:43.09,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Thanks for keeping me company. I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.34,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.31,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'll see you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.27,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.08,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,I made the stars fall again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:21.53,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,There were so many... today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.61,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Hei, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:38.51,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.74,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Oh, no. It's starting to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.93,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I told you we wouldn't be able to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:58.40,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Weren't you looking up at the sky a minute ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.87,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:03.44,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Detectives have to be realistic in order to do their jobs, Kiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:10.25,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Whether the stars disappear or a weird gate appears,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:15.01,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,no matter how many changes occur in the  environment, people won't change how they live their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:19.42,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Boss, you're pretty cool today, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:21.22,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Don't fall for me, Kiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:29.07,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,All's right with the world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.38,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Hei, stay away from your apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:40.03,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.53,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Don't ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:47.37,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.29,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Huang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:51.13,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It looks like we were thrown out of the syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.14,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.69,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:59.06,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Hei, about the disappearance of the gate in South America...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.24,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Are you hiding something from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:14.44,DTB-Default,Contractor,0,0,0,,No hard feelings, BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.46,DTB-Default,Contractor,0,0,0,,I'm just following orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:27.81,DTB-Default,Wei,0,0,0,,A manipulator of gravity, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:32.90,DTB-Default,Wei,0,0,0,,Supernaturals with power tend to get  cocky and forget about their surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:34.09,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:38.62,DTB-Default,Wei,0,0,0,,Hey, take it easy. There's no need to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:42.54,DTB-Default,Wei,0,0,0,,I was sent by Amber as a messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:47.45,DTB-Default,Wei,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting for you inside the gate, BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:51.61,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Bullshit! It isn't a place you can enter that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:54.86,DTB-Default,Wei,0,0,0,,That's why I shall act as your guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.21,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Did you think we'd fall for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.12,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:58.67,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Hei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:03.89,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened at Heaven's Gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:08.18,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,including the reason why my sister Pai disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:11.25,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Amber's the only one who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.08,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.50,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,you want to find out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:17.16,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:22.64,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Meet with Amber and talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.32,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Huang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.47,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hop in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:30.85,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I'll take you as far as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:36.67,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Why?  Why are our superiors mobilizing without notifying us first?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:40.23,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,There was a possibility of some kind of intervention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:40.90,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Intervention?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:42.39,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.84,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:53.17,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Dad, what is it? I'm a little busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.39,DTB-Default,Naoyasu,0,0,0,,Evacuate as soon as you can, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.50,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Evacuate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.22,DTB-Default,Naoyasu,0,0,0,,I'll explain the details later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.99,DTB-Default,Naoyasu,0,0,0,,Leave Tokyo at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:03.05,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What's going on? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:14.02,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,whatever happened in South  America is about to take place here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:20.82,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,At the moment, we have two primary objectives:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:24.11,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Lead the dolls into the gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:26.41,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,and destroy the particle accelerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.21,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:45.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost here, the beginning of the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkle, twinkle, sparkle, sparkle,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:52.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,the stars shine, and fall to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:57.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Boom, boom, the place where they fall
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:21:01.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,is inside a mist, where nothing can be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:04.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The mist inside men's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:08.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait until you see what is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:10.35,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,580)}Episode Twenty-Four Meteor Shower...